title: Photos: Alabama runs over A&M in top-10 showdown; Tide tops Aggies 41-23
text: Alabama Crimson Tide running back Derrick Henry (2) rushes the ball in the second quarter during an NCAA football game between Alabama and Texas A&M at Kyle Field in College Station, Texas Saturday October 17, 2015. Texas A&M Aggies lost to Alabama Crimson Tide 23-41. (Andy Jacobsohn/The Dallas Morning News)
